| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2603 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 124e31da-ca6c-5c25-806f-f73dfa1038f3"
